# Scenario 001 - SSH Brute Force Detection

## Objective

Validate the complete DarkForest SOC detection chain by generating a controlled SSH password attack from the attacker workstation and observing the resulting telemetry in Splunk.

---

## Attack Path

```text
Attacker VM
(Debian 13 + Exegol)
        │
        ▼
Ubuntu24 SSH Service
(10.10.6.3)
        │
        ▼
/var/log/auth.log
        │
        ▼
Splunk Universal Forwarder
        │
        ▼
Splunk Index: linux
        │
        ▼
Linux Monitoring Dashboard
```

---

