## Splunk Data Source

Forwarded file:

```text
/var/log/auth.log
```

Universal Forwarder configuration:

```ini
[monitor:///var/log/auth.log]
disabled = false
index = linux
sourcetype = linux_auth
```

---

## Splunk Dashboard Validation

The following dashboard panels successfully detected the activity:

### Failed SSH Logins

Detected multiple failed authentication attempts.

### Successful SSH Logins

Detected successful authentication after password discovery.

### Attacking IPs

Displayed attacker source:

```text
10.10.4.1
```

### Attack Timeline

Displayed attack sequence:

```text
Failed password
Failed password
Failed password
Accepted password
```

### Latest Events

Displayed raw authentication events from auth.log.

